<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" xmlns:og="http://opengraphprotocol.org/schema/" xmlns:fb="https://www.facebook.com/2008/fbml">
<head>
    <title>Try out the KPCC.org Beta!</title>
	<%= render "shared/header/header_js" %>
	<%= render "shared/header/opengraph" %>
	<%= csrf_meta_tags %>
</head>
<body class="minimal">
	<header>
		<div class="container-fluid">
			<h3 id="site-title"><a href="/">KPCC 89.3</a></h3>
			<a class="home-link" href="/">Back to KPCC Home</a>
		</div>
	</header>

	<div class="content-container">
		<div id="beta" class="container-fluid">
			<div class="box">
				<h3 class="logo-mark-sm">Get a sneak peek at the new KPCC.org!</h3>
				<p>We're hard at work on a redesign of the KPCC website, and want your feedback on our early progress. By clicking the "opt in" button below, you'll start getting a sneak peak of the redesign as you browse KPCC.org. </p>
				<p>A few things to note before you check out the beta:</p>
				<ul>
					<li><strong>The site is a work in progress.</strong><br />We haven't redesigned every section of the site yet, so in places where the redesign isn't complete, you'll still see pages in the current design.</li>
					<li><strong>Tell us what you think.</strong><br />We love to hear what you think. Use the feedback button at the bottom of every page to share questions, ideas or problems.</li>
					<li><strong>Opt out at any time.</strong><br />There's a link at the top of every page that will exit you out of the beta and return you to the current site design.</li>
				</ul>
					<p class="beta-button">
						<a href="#" class="btn primary" id="beta-button">Configuring</a><br />
						<a href="/" id="beta-home" style="display:none;">Take me to the Home Page!</a>
					</p>
			</div>
		
			<div class="floating-shadow">&nbsp;</div>
	  	</div> <!-- container-fluid -->
	</div>

	<footer>
		<div class="container-fluid">
			<ul>
				<li><a href="/terms/">Terms &amp; Conditions</a></li>
				<li><a href="/privacy/">Privacy</a></li>
				<li><a href="/web_site_feedback">Website Feedback</a></li>
				<li>Copyright 2001 &copy; Southern California Public Radio</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</footer>


<% content_for :footerjss do %>
	var beta = new scpr.BetaToggle()
<% end %>

<%= render "shared/footer/footer_js" %>
</body>
</html>